Robert D. Walker https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Robert_D._Walker 0 Robert Donald Walker (June 18, 1888 – March 4, 1954) was an American film actor. He appeared in 215 films between 1913 and 1953. He was born in Bethlehem, Pennsylvania and died in Los Angeles, California. Robert_Donald_Walker ( June_18_,_1888 – March_4_,_1954 ) was an_American_film_actor .
